Class RevisionMarkAuthorTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwpf.model.RevisionMarkAuthorTable

  • @Internal
public final class RevisionMarkAuthorTable
extends java.lang.Object
    String table containing the names of authors of revision marks, e-mails and comments in this document.(包含本文档中修订标记、电子邮件和评论的作者姓名的字符串表。)
    Author:
    Ryan Lauck
